Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
2020 Talks covers the contenders of all parties as they court voters at intimate events in coffee shops, bars, and homes. 

The newscast focuses on important national issues and the spirit of the people who are vetting these candidates.
